{id:"course2",emoji:"💰",title:"28-Day Course: Affiliate Marketing",color:"#10b981",badge:"NEW",lessons:[ 
{title:"Day 1 — Your Affiliate Business Overview",body:"WELCOME TO 28-DAY AFFILIATE MARKETING MASTERY\n\nAffiliate marketing is the simplest business model online.\n\nHOW IT WORKS:\n1. You sign up to promote a product (free)\n2. You get a unique tracking link\n3. You share that link in your videos and content\n4. Someone clicks and buys\n5. The company pays YOU a commission automatically\n\nYOU DO NOT:\n• Handle shipping\n• Deal with customer service\n• Hold inventory\n• Create the product\n\nYOUR 5 ACTIVE PROGRAMS:\n1. Vidnoz — 50% commission — $25+ per sale\n2. InVideo — 30% commission — $15+ per sale\n3. MailerLite — $140 flat per referral\n4. CapCut — Revenue share\n5. Udemy — 15% per course sold\n\nYOUR CONTENT ENGINE (already built):\n• 5 anchor videos per week\n• Affiliate link in every description\n• Email list building through every video\n\nDAY 1 ACTION: Log into all 5 affiliate dashboards and write down your current earnings for each one."}, 
{title:"Day 2-7 — The Influencer Promo Formula",body:"THE FORMULA THAT CONVERTS VIEWERS TO BUYERS\n\nEvery affiliate promo follows this exact structure:\n\n1. HOOK — Pain Point (first 3 seconds)\n'If you are still editing videos by hand you are wasting 6 hours a week...'\n\n2. STORY — Relatable Experience\n'I used to spend my whole Sunday editing one video...'\n\n3. DEMO — What The Product Does\n'Then I found Vidnoz AI and now I create a professional video in under 10 minutes...'\n\n4. PROOF — Specific Result\n'My last video got 2,400 views in 48 hours and I spent 8 minutes making it...'\n\n5. CTA — Exactly What To Do\n'Click the link in my description — try Vidnoz free for 7 days. No credit card needed.'\n\nYOUR ANCHORS DELIVER THIS:\n• Alisha: High energy hooks and FOMO-driven promos\n• Lisa: Credible expert endorsements\n• Susan: Warm story-driven recommendations\n• Paul: Trusted grandfather seal of approval\n\nBECKY WRITES THESE FOR YOU.\nJust tell Becky: 'Write an influencer promo for Vidnoz using Alisha. Hook about wasted editing time. 45 seconds.'"}, 
{title:"Day 8-14 — Building Your Email List",body:"YOUR EMAIL LIST IS YOUR MOST VALUABLE ASSET\n\nWhy? Because YouTube can delete your channel. TikTok can ban you. But nobody can take your email list.\n\nMAILERLITE SETUP (FREE up to 1,000 subscribers):\n1. Go to mailerlite.com — sign up free\n2. Create a landing page: 'Get My FREE AI Video Toolkit'\n3. Add a simple email capture form\n4. Connect to an automation sequence\n5. Share the landing page link in every video description\n\nYOUR 3-EMAIL WELCOME SEQUENCE:\nEmail 1 (Instant): Subject: 'Here is your free AI toolkit'\n- Deliver the free resource they signed up for\n- Introduce yourself and your show\n\nEmail 2 (Day 2): Subject: 'The tool that changed everything for me'\n- Tell your Vidnoz story\n- Include your affiliate link naturally\n\nEmail 3 (Day 4): Subject: 'I made 5 videos last Monday (here is how)'\n- Share your batch production workflow\n- Strong CTA: try Vidnoz free link\n\nEVERY MAILERLITE REFERRAL = $140\nGet 3 people to sign up for MailerLite and you have made $420 with zero product to sell.\n\nBECKY: 'Write a 3-email welcome sequence for people who downloaded my free AI Video Toolkit. They are small business owners in Southeast Texas.'"}, 
{title:"Day 15-21 — Content That Converts",body:"THE 5 CONTENT TYPES THAT DRIVE AFFILIATE SALES\n\n1. TUTORIAL VIDEOS (highest converter)\n'How to create a professional business video in 10 minutes'\nShow the tool in action. Link in description.\nConversion rate: 8-15%\n\n2. COMPARISON VIDEOS\n'Best AI video tools for small businesses 2026'\nYour affiliate tools win the comparison. Honest but strategic.\nConversion rate: 12-20%\n\n3. RESULTS VIDEOS\n'I made 5 videos in one day using this AI tool'\nReal results. Real numbers. People want proof.\nConversion rate: 10-18%\n\n4. PROBLEM/SOLUTION VIDEOS\n'Why your business videos look amateur (and the free fix)'\nIdentify the pain. Present your affiliate tool as the solution.\nConversion rate: 6-12%\n\n5. NEWS-STYLE REVIEW\n'This AI tool is changing how small businesses make videos'\nLisa or Susan delivers it as a news segment. Credibility.\nConversion rate: 5-10%\n\nBATCH THESE WITH BECKY:\nTell Becky: 'Plan 5 affiliate videos for Vidnoz this week — one tutorial, one comparison, one results video, one problem/solution, one Lisa news review. Write all 5 scripts.'"}, 
{title:"Day 22-28 — Scale to $3,000/Month",body:"YOUR PATH TO $3,000 MONTHLY AFFILIATE INCOME\n\nMATH BREAKDOWN:\n\nVIDNOZ ($25/sale × 50% commission):\nTarget: 20 sales/month\nIncome: $500/month\nHow: 1 dedicated Vidnoz video per week\n\nINVIDEO ($15/sale × 30% commission):\nTarget: 20 sales/month\nIncome: $300/month\nHow: InVideo mention in every Alisha video\n\nMAILERLITE ($140 flat per referral):\nTarget: 5 referrals/month\nIncome: $700/month\nHow: Susan Monday builds email list content\n\nCAPCUT + UDEMY:\nTarget: 30 combined sales/month\nIncome: $200/month\nHow: Natural mentions in production workflow videos\n\nLOCAL BUSINESS CLIENTS:\nTarget: 3 clients at $300 average\nIncome: $900/month\nHow: Your 60-second pitch + 2 free sample videos\n\nTOTAL: $2,600/month passive + local clients\n\nHIT THIS IN 6 MONTHS WITH:\n• 5 videos per week (your Wan2.2 Factory)\n• Affiliate link in every description\n• Email list growing weekly\n• 1 new local client pitch per week\n\nYOU HAVE THE SYSTEM. NOW EXECUTE."} 
]}, 
