{id:"course3",emoji:"🤖",title:"28-Day Course: AI Agent Business",color:"#a78bfa",badge:"NEW",lessons:[ 
{title:"Day 1 — Your Agent Operating System",body:"WELCOME TO 28-DAY AI AGENT BUSINESS BUILDING\n\nAn Agent OS is a command center where multiple AI agents work simultaneously on your business — while you manage as CEO.\n\nTHINK OF IT LIKE THIS:\nYou are the CEO. Your agents are your team.\n• Content Agent — writes all scripts and copy\n• Video Agent — manages Wan2.2 Factory workflow\n• Research Agent — tracks trends and competitors\n• Email Agent — writes outreach and follow-ups\n• Social Agent — creates hooks and captions\n• Strategy Agent — plans your business growth\n\nYOUR AGENT STACK (100% FREE):\n• Claude Sonnet — primary agent brain (API)\n• Groq Llama 3.3 70B — fast free agent (gsk_ key)\n• Google Gemini 2.5 Flash — free via AI Studio\n• Free LLM API — 800M tokens/month free\n• Agent OS Dashboard — your command center\n\nWHAT YOUR AGENTS DO FOR YOU:\n• Write all scripts automatically\n• Generate Wan2.2 scene prompts\n• Research affiliate programs\n• Write all email sequences\n• Create social media content\n• Plan your weekly strategy\n\nDAY 1 ACTION: Open the Agent OS app. Launch all agents. See them run simultaneously."}, 
{title:"Day 2-7 — Running Multiple Agents",body:"HOW TO RUN AGENTS SIMULTANEOUSLY\n\nIn your Agent OS Multi-Agent Command Center:\n\nMETHOD 1 — BROADCAST (all agents at once)\nType one task in the broadcast bar.\nHit the ALL button.\nAll 6 agents work on it from their own perspective simultaneously.\n\nEXAMPLE BROADCAST:\n'AffiliateMediaHub Studio is launching a new Vidnoz affiliate campaign. Each agent provide your best output for your role.'\n\nRESULT:\n• Content Agent writes the scripts\n• Video Agent writes Wan2.2 scene prompts\n• Research Agent finds Vidnoz competitor data\n• Email Agent writes the email sequence\n• Social Agent writes the captions and hooks\n• Strategy Agent builds the 4-week campaign plan\n\nAll 6 done in under 2 minutes.\n\nMETHOD 2 — INDIVIDUAL AGENT CHAT\nClick any agent card → opens direct chat\nWork one-on-one for deeper tasks\n\nMETHOD 3 — LAUNCH ALL\nHit the big LAUNCH ALL button\nEach agent runs their default weekly task automatically\n\nYOUR TIME SAVED: What used to take 6 hours of manual work now takes 4 minutes."}, 
{title:"Day 8-14 — Agent Memory System",body:"BUILDING AN AGENT MEMORY SYSTEM\n\nThe most powerful thing about an Agent OS is memory. Your agents remember everything about your business and improve over time.\n\nYOUR MEMORY VAULT CONTAINS:\n• Hub Engine v4 Stack details\n• Wan2.2 Factory workflow steps\n• Cast schedule (Susan Mon, Alisha Wed, Paul Thu, Lisa Fri+Sat)\n• All anchor descriptions and styles\n• Affiliate program details and commission rates\n• Your business goals and monthly targets\n• Past campaign results\n\nADD MEMORIES AS YOU GO:\nAfter every successful campaign — add it to Memory Vault\nAfter every video that performs well — add what worked\nAfter every client meeting — add what they need\n\nWHY THIS MATTERS:\nWithout memory: Every chat starts from zero. You explain yourself every time.\nWith memory: Agents already know your full business context. They produce better output immediately.\n\nFUTURE: Obsidian Integration\nConnect your Agent OS to Obsidian for a local knowledge base that every agent reads automatically. Your agents get smarter every week.\n\nDAY 8-14 ACTION: Add 10 memories to your Memory Vault. Make them detailed and specific."}, 
{title:"Day 15-21 — Hermes Agent Hub",body:"HERMES AGENT HUB — YOUR LOCAL AGENT MANAGER\n\nHermes is an open-source agent app that runs autonomously on your computer — handling tasks, saving outputs, and building skills.\n\nWHAT HERMES DOES:\n• Kanban task board — assign tasks to agents\n• Skills system — builds reusable workflows\n• Goal mode — 'Write me an SEO blog post' and it runs start to finish\n• Saves all outputs to your workspace\n• Runs on schedule — automated background tasks\n\nSETUP FOR YOUR STUDIO:\n1. Open Hermes in your Terminal\n2. At API key prompt — use your Groq key (gsk_...)\n3. Model: llama-3.3-70b-versatile (128K context, free)\n4. Create your first skill: Wan2.2 Video Production\n5. Add your cast schedule as a knowledge file\n\nHERMES + WAN2.2 FACTORY:\nSet Hermes on a schedule timer\nEvery Monday: Auto-generate Susan's script\nEvery Wednesday: Auto-generate Alisha's script\nEvery Thursday: Auto-generate Paul's script\nEvery Friday: Auto-generate Lisa's script\n\nBrad (a real user) built his entire autonomous content platform on Hermes running on a small local model called Bonsai. If he can do it — you can do it.\n\nDAY 15: Install Hermes. Add Groq key. Get it active. Then come back to Day 16."}, 
{title:"Day 22-28 — Full Autonomous System",body:"WEEK 4 — YOUR FULLY AUTONOMOUS BUSINESS MACHINE\n\nBy now you have:\n• Agent OS running 6 simultaneous agents\n• Hermes managing scheduled tasks\n• Memory Vault with 10+ business memories\n• Free LLM API providing 800M tokens/month\n• Wan2.2 Factory producing 5 videos/week\n• Affiliate links in all content\n\nYOUR AUTONOMOUS WEEKLY ROUTINE:\n\nMONDAY 9AM (Automatic — Hermes):\n• Susan script generated\n• ElevenLabs voice prompt ready\n• Wan2.2 scene prompts generated\n• Social captions written for all platforms\n\nWEDNESDAY 9AM (Automatic):\n• Alisha script + scenes + captions\n\nTHURSDAY 9AM (Automatic):\n• Paul script + scenes + captions\n\nFRIDAY 9AM (Automatic):\n• Lisa script + scenes + captions\n• Lisa Saturday affiliate script\n\nYOUR JOB AS CEO:\n✓ Review outputs (15 minutes)\n✓ Run FFmpeg merge (5 minutes per video)\n✓ CapCut captions (10 minutes per video)\n✓ Post to platforms (10 minutes per video)\n✓ Total: 2 hours per week instead of 30+\n\nTHIS IS THE SYSTEM. This is what Julian Goldie built. This is what Brad built. Now YOU have it too."} 
]}, 
